title: WATCH: Youth football team does 'Whip' and the 'Nae Nae'
text:
WATCH: Youth football team does 'Whip' and the 'Nae Nae' Avery Stone, USA TODAY 1:17 p.m. EDT October 8, 2015 During halftime of a high school football game, the Milford Mighty Mights had a mini-scrimmage, and couldn’t help dancing along to Silento’s hit song. (Photo: Laure Farrell, YouTube) CONNECT TWEET LINKEDIN COMMENT EMAIL MORE 
Sometimes, it seems like the entire sports world is doing the “Whip” and the “Nae Nae.” But these youth football players from Milford, Mass., just out-danced all their competition. 
During halftime of a high school football game, the Milford Mighty Mights had a mini-scrimmage, and couldn’t help dancing along to Silento’s hit song. And it was absolutely adorable.
